  "title": "Sales Trader, Institutional Equities",
  "description": "<p>A leading Asia-focused brokerage is looking to hire a Sales Trader to join its Institutional Equities platform in Singapore.<br /><br />This role sits within a regional sales trading setup and focuses on supporting institutional and hedge fund clients across execution, flow discussion and day-to-day market interaction. The successful hire will work closely with senior sales traders, trading desks and internal partners across the region, with clear exposure to ASEAN client activity.<br /><br /><u>What the role involves</u></p><ul><li>Handling institutional equity orders with a strong focus on execution quality</li><li>Engaging clients on market conditions, liquidity and flow dynamics</li><li>Supporting senior sales traders on key accounts and coverage responsibilities</li><li>Working closely with internal trading, sales and research teams</li><li>Contributing to broader client engagement and wallet-share initiatives over time</li></ul><p><br /><u>What they’re looking for</u></p><ul><li>3 - 8 years of experience in equity sales trading within a brokerage environment</li><li>Sound understanding of cash equities and the trade lifecycle</li><li>Comfortable speaking with institutional clients and responding to market-driven queries</li><li>Strong communication skills and a collaborative working style</li><li>Mandarin proficiency required due to existing client coverage</li></ul><p><br />R22104718<br />BeathChapman Pte Ltd<br />Licence no. 16S8112</p>",
  "minimumYearsExperience": 3,
